ate strategy: skips primary workflow, directly runs dynamic-access coverage improvement on existing tests.\",\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1448:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:764:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\",\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1449:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:779:    \"description\": \"Library-update bulk dynamic-access strategy: runs only the optimistic full-report workflow against existing tests, without per-class refinement.\",\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1450:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:784:      \"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration-update.md\"\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1451:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:799:    \"description\": \"Library-update composite strategy: bulk dynamic-access coverage in one broad pass first, then per-class iterative refinement of any stragglers. Mirrors the iterative library-update strategy but starts with a faster bulk pass.\",\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1452:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:805:      \"optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/optimistic-dynamic-access-iteration-update.md\",\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1453:  ../../../strategie