prov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1508:  ../../../DEVELOPING.md:101:  [--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access] \\\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1509:  ../../../DEVELOPING.md:126:- `--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access` keeps generated tests for dynamic-access workflows even if no dynamic-access call sites are covered.\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1510:  ../../../DEVELOPING.md:386:coordinates, active dynamic-access classes, source-context paths, and Gradle\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1511:  ../../../DEVELOPING.md:421:The `dynamic_access_iterative` workflow improves metadata accuracy by using the `generateDynamicAccessCoverageReport` Gradle task to identify which dynamic-access call sites (reflection, JNI, resources, serialization) are not yet covered by the generated tests. Instead of generating tests blindly, the workflow iterates class-by-class, sending the agent targeted prompts with the exact uncovered call sites for each class. After each attempt, the report is regenerated and coverage deltas are computed to decide whether to retry the same class or move on.\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1512:  ../../../DEVELOPING.md:452:Composite strategies (run a primary workflow, then refine dynamic-access coverage):\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1513:  ../../../DEVELOPING.md:459:#### Running a dynamic-access strategy\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1514:  ../../../DEVELOPING.md:482:see `docs/workflows/dynamic-access.md`.\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1515:  ../../../git_scripts/make_pr_improve_coverage.py:141:This PR improves dynamic-access coverage for {coordinates} by generating additional tests.\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1516:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:62:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1517:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:81:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1518:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:100:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1519:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:119:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1520:  ../../../strategies/predefined_strategies.json:139:      \"dynamic-access-iteration\": \"prompt_templates/dynamic_access/dynamic-access-iteration.md\"\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk15on:1.48/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-06-07T18-04-20-830653Z.log:1521:  ../../../strategies/predefined_