ires it. I could consider including a note like \\\"leave uncovered with explanation\\\" in the final report if we can’t proceed due to an Unknown Source. Maybe some code changes are needed. I wonder if it could be beneficial to add a second test with the Bouncy Castle Provider JCA to generate an actual key and verify that the serialized key class is specifically BCDSAPrivateKey. This feels like a better approach since it highlights the public API and the dynamic private methods.\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_05fe2a3f75903d0c016a25b3b8b3508197ad4e66ba18e2d157\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"content\\\":[],\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABqJbPMt8GadQ8WxTO7cBaH9c24yeh3Arc1SXlBgcTcLw8W91lvkyrJLKC2PQpkMcwkGR0BV0IsvQSzoP_u3gRe1rKsoSlyI1LynWs5K0L6gXoL9iQIa2PQYybQ38Pgh4Xn-NY2-0wpHRFlh5adE73xQHXbAPw2kwoWHX4ig-sDZMoCDCD6Pe4aUACBQId89fmiEy0UlAfC3gm_fv4fO9nuM2wJvurucRsyJrcfsKBJdOeWULHuhLfvthdrmthvEbrVBXKCHlxieHkQMLS9kk-sX0Rer3I6TRqFMBRrfy7Xvd-771Sy8YkxJsU_6kjQ3qFHCCYlKmPFR8m42wNSdGoWljVrmsKtFvawShLVlJp0L0vuwmaBlTx2hkYrom1NRJ0vS6falxm_DE1TuWJQE7B0-1-vnVLUP-dvRnTpaKaZkemlbuW2Gk1JQRXmuZ_6e4QijjXCG9BGHEJOQYS5WEUwy7OlN8gd2GZhlLMlMYFvdu6mObQt0dNsVahtnNKothooGE9bg3Dn0ZMz3BnC5hYporRD2Laf-I_L1zXPqN9fHE1q_aSUc1Dg8xWA7tt2MEiadyjytasy6H3VfoztuNDvFS7BDpPS1eDGFaZA03sdA9Y5LT4NMPQnI6FmuyucfDjya03n1o4WGtH15xRx-D-3JOa11aFd0hltXk9mcOftjp9IJRMb16klLAY82bOIOhxoyWG_iN0Zkw9LSJk0UAt0yyVY6HLNvD5zIKsBG9iPxabbnHmrd6GMOeEjJjndmx6OOUJJNldi6TL3IuLQIwTmgV7KDWl_lE-iW4AzuN45hhsRkI7LpwGVrVygUXQNq130Yc_-zkGkIrbxXXIuS4Tq7U3MsBfpSLjikd6UcOBMo8IOVnxhAWcA-_F39Elx0pPUGSAEHIM8uiXTn8fYHZy0apcc8kH3DTNyl4RYRFfpGdESsqACmoV6bi-AX-SF17JOYhRQmiuJCvKovMNQbfolhJsuO7cPt0JETGaYtOIOIkie-xsXXAWKo9BJcDQ_VoSULq9O5k8ZnUU0JVS8gJxvvkOu5ZO5eDV7zhE5DJs0KleUzXgssbCKbbaQmaHRPlP1LdlUTC4S6x7IioD07DkomsO6uj3Hk_64TiNjouZtvV8MjVQdMt8M_xD9Xv_7Y_lB0tL5JINI9TMFZGVxcmrIqLcJ4WwPa8Ye-bN7uwkiaIdNmuXQdmGpKRMW0wS71xGDeFX7IdXSktAtI71g0I1wR-QdLIEXM-o6iOaA_WY62NZQlFsUIemcdsk11kIXT9fOFTv2VV1rdePy9pzFp-2QN-sQWuebxZ6a3tomIpMO58SHQ