ower coverage percentage for the requested version is blocking unless the PR gives a concrete explanation, such as upstream removal of reachable dynamic-access sites or an intentionally narrower supported surface.\\n./skills/review-library-update-request/SKILL.md:64:   - Do not apply the `library-new-request` rule that dynamic-access coverage must be above 20%.\\n./skills/review-library-update-request/SKILL.md:122:- For coverage percentage drops: say that `library-update-request` PRs must not reduce dynamic-access coverage percentage between versions, cite old and new percentages, and ask for restored coverage or a concrete explanation.\\n./stats/com.github.ben-manes.caffeine/caffeine/3.1.2/stats.json:8:          \\\"coveredCalls\\\" : 8,\\n./stats/com.github.ben-manes.caffeine/caffeine/3.1.2/stats.json:13:      \\\"coveredCalls\\\" : 8,\\n./stats/org.jboss.arquillian.container/arquillian-container-test-impl-base/1.1.10.Final/stats.json:8:          \\\"coveredCalls\\\" : 16,\\n./stats/org.jboss.arquillian.container/arquillian-container-test-impl-base/1.1.10.Final/stats.json:13:          \\\"coveredCalls\\\" : 1,\\n./stats/org.jboss.arquillian.container/arquillian-container-test-impl-base/1.1.10.Final/stats.json:18:      \\\"coveredCalls\\\" : 17,\\n./stats/com.github.ben-manes.caffeine/caffeine/2.9.3/stats.json:8:          \\\"coveredCalls\\\" : 14,\\n./stats/com.github.ben-manes.caffeine/caffeine/2.9.3/stats.json:13:      \\\"coveredCalls\\\" : 14,\\n./stats/org.jboss.arquillian.container/arquillian-container-test-impl-base/1.1.10.Final/execution-metrics.json:17:            \\\"coveredCalls\\\": 16,\\n./stats/org.jboss.arquillian.container/arquillian-container-test-impl-base/1.1.10.Final/execution-metrics.json:22:            \\\"coveredCalls\\\": 1,\\n./stats/org.jboss.arquillian.container/arquillian-container-test-impl-base/1.1.10.Final/execution-metrics.json:27:        \\\"coveredCalls\\\": 17,\\n./forge/forge_metadata.py:3024:    \\\"\\\"\\\"Load dynamic-access 